# Payroll Domain Rules

- Treat payroll data as sensitive; avoid unnecessary data exposure.
- Keep payroll run lifecycle explicit: draft, review/approve, finalized, published.
- Recalculate and persist run totals after item-level changes.
- For salary edits, enforce non-negative numeric validation.
- In UI, show clear status badges and operation feedback for payroll actions.
